FeedPackage.Description: This library contains a custom 404 handler for your EPiServer project. It will also handle more 404 cases than the built-in handler. It also includes a Custom Redirect Gadget (for EPiServer Online Center) for editors to add redirects. The 404 handler logs all 404 errors and present them in a list in the gadget, which will allow editors to easily add redirects based on the logged errors.
